Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's inauguration preparations
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407bnq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Jan 1977
Arguments flare over preparations for Jimmy Carter's presidential inauguration. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.